item.title: CVE-2023-3596|2024-08-02T07:01:56.685Z -- rockwell%20automation -- 1756-en4tr%20series%20a
item.description: Where this vulnerability exists in the Rockwell Automation 1756-EN4* Ethernet/IP communication products, it could allow a malicious user to cause a denial of service by asserting the target system through maliciously crafted CIP messages.
